  <summary date="2023-08-11T14:45:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Stealthing Act of 2022 

This bill establishes a civil action for the nonconsensual removal of a sexual protection barrier (e.g., a condom). A person may recover compensatory and punitive damages, injunctive and declaratory relief, and such other relief as a court may deem appropriate.</summary>
